4. Baseball ‚Äì Joueurs canadiens
Jeux de donn√©es¬†: Lahman::People, Lahman::Batting (package Lahman).

Obtiens la liste des joueurs n√©s au Canada (birthCountry).
Calcule leur moyenne au b√¢ton (H/AB) en fusionnant People ‚ÜîÔ∏é Batting sur playerID.







Tip





library(dplyr)
library(Lahman)

can_players &lt;- People |&gt;
  filter(birthCountry == "Canada") |&gt;
  select(playerID, nameFirst, nameLast)

can_stats &lt;- can_players |&gt;
  inner_join(select(Batting, playerID, H, AB), by = "playerID") |&gt;
  group_by(playerID, nameFirst, nameLast) |&gt;
  summarise(avg = sum(H, na.rm = TRUE) / sum(AB, na.rm = TRUE),
            .groups = "drop")

5. Pr√©noms & Premi√®re lettre
Jeu de donn√©es¬†: babynames::babynames (package babynames). Cr√©e un tibble alphabet comportant la premi√®re lettre (initial) et sa cat√©gorie (¬´¬†A‚ÄëM¬†¬ª, ¬´¬†N‚ÄëZ¬†¬ª). Ajoute la cat√©gorie √† babynames, puis compte les naissances par cat√©gorie en 2010.






Tip





library(dplyr)
library(babynames)

alphabet &lt;- tibble::tibble(
  initial = LETTERS,
  group   = if_else(initial &lt;= "M", "A-M", "N-Z")
)

babynames_2010 &lt;- babynames |&gt;
  filter(year == 2010) |&gt;
  mutate(initial = substr(name, 1, 1)) |&gt;
  inner_join(alphabet, by = "initial") |&gt;
  group_by(group) |&gt;
  summarise(total = sum(n))

7. Pizza¬†Ratings
Jeux de donn√©es¬†: fivethirtyeight::pizza et fivethirtyeight::pizza_places (package fivethirtyeight). Associe chaque √©valuation (pizza) √† son restaurant (pizza_places) via place_id et trouve la note moyenne (rating) par state.






Tip





library(dplyr)
library(fivethirtyeight)

pizza_avg_state &lt;- pizza |&gt;
  inner_join(pizza_places, by = "place_id") |&gt;
  group_by(state) |&gt;
  summarise(mean_rating = mean(rating, na.rm = TRUE))

8. ONU ‚Äì Votes & R√©solutions
Jeux de donn√©es¬†: unvotes::un_votes, unvotes::un_roll_calls (package unvotes). Relie chaque vote (un_votes) √† la description de la r√©solution (un_roll_calls) via rcid. √ânum√®re les cinq pays ayant vot√© le plus souvent ¬´¬†no¬†¬ª entre 2000 et 2010.






Tip





library(dplyr)
library(unvotes)

votes_desc &lt;- un_votes |&gt;
  inner_join(un_roll_calls, by = "rcid") |&gt;
  filter(year &gt;= 2000, year &lt;= 2010, vote == "no") |&gt;
  count(country, sort = TRUE) |&gt;
  slice_head(n = 5)
